@desc Purchase Label with Rate ID
@optional {custom_field1: str # Optional - Value will be saved in the shipment's advanced_options > custom_field1, custom_field2: str # Optional - Value will be saved in the shipment's advanced_options > custom_field2, custom_field3: str # Optional - Value will be saved in the shipment's advanced_options > custom_field3}
@returns(200) The requested object creation was a success.
